---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us - TaxPortal" description="Learn about TaxPortal's mission to provide comprehensive international tax information and calculators.">
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink"><span data-i18n="taxportal_home">TaxPortal</span></h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-body dark:text-muted">
          TaxPortal is a comprehensive international tax platform providing accurate, up-to-date tax information and calculators for individuals and businesses worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">
              To make international tax information accessible, understandable, and actionable for everyone. We believe that navigating complex tax systems should not be a barrier to global opportunity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Our Vision</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">
              A world where anyone can confidently understand and comply with tax obligations in any country, regardless of their background or expertise.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline bg-canvas-soft dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-primary">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Why Choose TaxPortal</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Global Coverage</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">Comprehensive tax data for over 10 countries and growing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Accurate Calculations</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">Professional-grade calculators with real-time results.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Free Access</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">All basic tools and guides are completely free to use.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Privacy First</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">No personal data required. All calculations happen in your browser.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Always Updated</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">Regular updates reflecting the latest tax laws and rates.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Expert Reviewed</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-body dark:text-muted">Content reviewed by tax professionals for accuracy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline dark:border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Our Commitment</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Accuracy</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">We strive to provide the most accurate and up-to-date tax information possible, sourced directly from official government resources.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Accessibility</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">We are committed to making tax information accessible to everyone, regardless of background or technical expertise.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Privacy</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">We do not collect or store personal information. All calculations are performed locally in your browser.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">Transparency</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">We clearly indicate when information is illustrative and should be verified with a qualified tax professional.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-hairline bg-canvas-soft dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-primary">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-body dark:text-muted leading-7">For inquiries, feedback, or suggestions, please reach out through our contact channels. We value your input in making TaxPortal better.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/countries" class="rounded-pill bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-on-primary transition hover:opacity-90 dark:bg-on-primary dark:text-primary"><span data-i18n="explore_countries">Explore Tax Information</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
